{"tid":2285407,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"鄧竟成：不同意警民關係變差說法","createTime":"2020-11-14T05:35:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-14T05:55:32.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c08c1e64827bc1df4a2381bccf8a67dbe5f02d4b","tid":2285407,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T05:35:05.000Z","msg":"香港友好協進會在灣仔擺設街站收集市民簽名，支持人大常委會取消4名議員資格的決定。全國政協委員、前香港警務處處長鄧竟成到場簽名。<br />\n<br />\n鄧竟成表示，自己是友好協進會的成員，自人大作出決定後，協進會便設街站進行聯署活動，讓市民有機會表達支持。他又說，政府對人大的決定已解釋得很清楚，是完全依法、合情、合理處理事情，希望議會可以回復正常運作，容許立法會議員能履行監察政府的職務。<br />\n<br />\n另外，鄧竟成認為現時警務處處長做得非常好，能清晰向市民解說工作，警隊在他領導下能迅速、積極及有效處理違法行為。他表示，不同意警民關係變差的說法，因為違法的人與警察關係一定不好。"},{"pid":"7d0a43760ec2c44f5653e24042a74b229509adc5","tid":2285407,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T05:35:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1559983-20201114.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1559983-20201114.htm&d=4dTSSGngnNsQf06YPjcNywEiaVT8aWta%2BTWQuzHxyy8%3D&h=a10922d7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1559983-20201114.htm&h=4ea70a72\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1559983-20201114.htm</a>"},{"pid":"e1f690aba2d33ec4dcbcdc5c03fe38b4c70e55c8","tid":2285407,"uid":218082,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T05:37:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B1LZZfk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB1LZZfk.jpg&h=8c309ebd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vzqfxAm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvzqfxAm.jpg&h=a7afa02b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n啱呀香港警察從來冇撚錯,香港人最鍾意警察<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f347518c0ab12263222ef001c046eea321db92f","tid":2285407,"uid":76804,"like":6,"dislike":0,"s